{"type": "article", "id": 7631, "title": "Loopwheel 减震车轮", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-23T07:06:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234833zenG95SDVhIyKJPU.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t英国发明家 Sam Pearce 设计了一种名为 Loopwheel 的减震车轮，他用轮轴与轮圈之间的弹簧片取代了传统的辐条，车轮采用碳纤维材料，大大减轻了车轮在崎岖不平的道路上行驶时容易受到的震动。Pearce 从婴儿车获得灵感，并用了四年多的时间来反复修改，车轮既可以用于普通的自行车，也可以用在轮椅上。去年这项设计获得了<a href=\"http://www.designsoftheyear.com/\" target=\"_blank\">“年度设计大奖”</a>，被认为革新了车轮的结构。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234830P205UeDzbluVxQKL.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234831vOjtTdw9uV5phQDb.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234832msMveYUwDbrQhXLl.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.40393013\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052348326slJMVIcoqEpbG5L.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.00571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052348337QA8bPIce9CuEqdT.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.61400651\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<br>\n\n\n"}